Get fonts from googlefonts and paste the Link into the top of header.php above the tachyons link 

And this in css 

webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased 
This is built into browsers to soften the edges of fonts 


body {
  /* here we use our main typeface and set it on our body tag */
  font-family: "Cardo", georgia, serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* wherever we use cardo class, we get cardo font */
.cardo {
  font-family: "Cardo", georgia, serif;
}

.archivo {
  font-family: "Archivo Black", sans-serif;
}

.tenor {
  font-family: "Tenor Sans", sans-serif;
}

.hero-heading,
.hero-subhead {
  font-size: 64px;
}
